{"tid":1469362,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【真。女權撚】墨西哥4黑警強姦少女　女群眾怒爆政府玻璃","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T01:51:15.000Z","uid":35519,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2641382b918fa881ae1f57f7ea25d74a14f8bb2d","tid":1469362,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/pofsmob4r9g31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fpofsmob4r9g31.jpg&h=e140bcc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/mvsnoticias/2019/08/03e91d8f-whatsapp-image-2019-08-12-at-15.36.49-1-1024x768.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Fmvsnoticias%2F2019%2F08%2F03e91d8f-whatsapp-image-2019-08-12-at-15.36.49-1-1024x768.jpeg&h=b1d1aad4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/mvsnoticias/2019/08/0c95c30b-whatsapp-image-2019-08-12-at-15.36.49-1024x768.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Fmvsnoticias%2F2019%2F08%2F0c95c30b-whatsapp-image-2019-08-12-at-15.36.49-1024x768.jpeg&h=22391b45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMEXICO CITY.<br />\n<br />\nWomen protesting on Monday at the Attorney General's Office (PGJ) in the capital <strong><ins>broke the windows and threw objects and paint inside </ins></strong>the unit in protest against the alleged sexual assaults committed by capital police.<br />\n<br />\nParticipants of the contingent <strong><ins>removed the security camera </ins></strong>that was placed in the main access to the building. <br />\n<br />\nAttendees of the protest throw slogans against the authorities while making pints inside the building located in the Doctores neighborhood, Cuauht&eacute;moc mayor's office.<br />\n<br />\nSo far <strong><ins>capital police have not intervened in the demonstration</ins></strong>, only the presence of elements attached to the Traffic Directorate who interrupt vehicular traffic is reported.<br />\n<br />\nThis, after it was reported that elements attached to the Secretariat of Citizen Security (SSC) <strong><ins>allegedly raped a minor in the mayor's office of Azcapotzalco</ins></strong>.<br />\n<br />\nThe women met at the premises of the SSC in the Liverpool street of the Roma neighborhood, where the head of the unit, Jes&uacute;s Orta, tried to establish a dialogue with the protesters, however, he was thrown a diamond in purple."},{"pid":"aff397848d991b732d961157ec7d7cd63bcae5bb","tid":1469362,"uid":35519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:34:21.000Z","msg":"完整影片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/CiroGomezL/status/1161121880553558016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCiroGomezL%2Fstatus%2F1161121880553558016&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0frgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=f5fd66b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCiroGomezL%2Fstatus%2F1161121880553558016&h=be6c50e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/CiroGomezL/status/1161121880553558016</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/mvsnoticias/2019/08/WhatsApp-Video-2019-08-12-at-15.37.45.mp4?_=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Fmvsnoticias%2F2019%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Video-2019-08-12-at-15.37.45.mp4%3F_%3D2&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0frgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=62549ce3\" target=\"_blank\">https://storage.googleapis.com/mvsnoticias/2019/08/WhatsApp-Video-2019-08-12-at-15.37.45.mp4?_=2</a>"},{"pid":"29092b92c42d6ea0815f8010424e953fd4189ad7","tid":1469362,"uid":35519,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:34:44.000Z","msg":"更多圖片：<br />\n<img src=\"https://imagenes.milenio.com/N14yTafVHic34Fw09xCe637Qf7k=/958x596/smart/https://www.milenio.com/uploads/media/2019/08/12/protesta-pgj-agresiones-policias-mujeres_0_68_1280_796.jpeg\"